Game class
----------

This event operates on an instance of the [game
class](Game_class "Game class") type {{{gameclass}}}

Description
-----------

Ensure the specified sound shader is loaded by the system. Prevents
cache hits when playing sound shaders.

Usage
-----

*void* cacheSoundShader( *string* **shaderName** )

Parameters
----------

-   [shaderName] - The name of the sound shader to cache.

